,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"760d463e5c3721f6913e83d66ee21b5398d501e7","tid":1554421,"uid":9049,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"PS<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=a074c1dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"f228a0a2db8a05508417b97e983b24077e774f60","tid":1554421,"uid":204429,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"講真 咁多即時爆炸嘅核彈唔炸人 仲要圍繞懷疑事件 如果炒車點搞？"},{"pid":"2f511974ead81e7a75ca91a297e142659f543739","tid":1554421,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95930b34334c14607b3d9edddbb3dfdc8e822af","tid":1554421,"uid":158613,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d1ab97bd34e4b2c3c06f53d31bda0576e7d95bf0","tid":1554421,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.